{"tid":1235602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(抵讚)反修例人士主動搬走路障物資清理垃圾　夏慤道全線重開","createTime":"2019-06-17T07:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T07:38:51.000Z","uid":50457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff748d8ba201c2b275555a954f410a37dfedee18","tid":1235602,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:37:32.000Z","msg":"部分留守金鐘夏慤道的反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威者，早上11時前轉往政總、立法會對出的添美道、立法會示威區及添馬公園一帶繼續聚集，警方其後重新開通夏慤道所有行車線。<br />\n<br />\n有反修例人士主動搬走路障同物資，又清理留下的垃圾。有贊成轉移陣地的示威者說，留守夏慤道的目的並非為了佔路，同時不想影響民生，因此贊成轉移其他地方，但強調並非撤退，重申政府必須撤回修例。<br />\n<br />\n但亦有示威者不認同，認為留守者氣勢好，佔據一條馬路影響亦不大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463346-20190617.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463346-20190617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=e414d55a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463346-20190617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=adaf18f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463346-20190617.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n傳媒好重要"},{"pid":"a2e8727ec1483a4dd403aebf8555e329279fb86a","tid":1235602,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:38:02.000Z","msg":"【反送中過後】屌你老味!!! 下星期就係《國歌法》二讀嘞....<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cPCuBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cPCuBS</a>"},{"pid":"0cee8ace58585e38a26ecb41ba4314cfc9d9d0a3","tid":1235602,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:38:03.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"3c417d059bf1d9c661976c131731a462a8e9d996","tid":1235602,"uid":133519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"打游擊戰最好，學毛澤東"}]}